OL,5, Martin Scorsese has lent his support to
OL,6, an Iranian director who has been jailed
OL,7, for screening a film at the Cannes Film
OL,8, Festival without government permission.
OL,10,FSaeed Roustaee, who premiered Leila's  
OL,11,FBrothers at the French festival in     
OL,12,F2022, was reportedly sentenced to six  
OL,13,Fmonths in prison by an Iranian court.  
OL,15,FFestival organisers said it was "a     
OL,16,Fserious violation of free speech".     
OL,18,FScorsese shared a petition calling for 
OL,19,F"justice" for Roustaee and the film's  
OL,20,Fproducer Javad Noruzbegi.              
